trans-unit.source: An intro to MapRouteFinder results
trans-unit.target: An intro to MapRouteFinder results

trans-unit.source: Here's how the classes for routes and directions are related:
trans-unit.target: Here's how the classes for routes and directions are related:

trans-unit.source: The [**MapRouteFinder**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636938) class has methods that get routes and directions.
trans-unit.target: The [**MapRouteFinder**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636938) class has methods that get routes and directions.

trans-unit.source: These methods return a [**MapRouteFinderResult**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636939).
trans-unit.target: These methods return a [**MapRouteFinderResult**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636939).

trans-unit.source: The [**MapRouteFinderResult**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636939) contains a [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) object.
trans-unit.target: The [**MapRouteFinderResult**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636939) contains a [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) object.

trans-unit.source: Access this object through the [**Route**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636940) property of the **MapRouteFinderResult**.
trans-unit.target: Access this object through the [**Route**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636940) property of the **MapRouteFinderResult**.

trans-unit.source: The [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) contains a collection of [**MapRouteLeg**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636955) objects.
trans-unit.target: The [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) contains a collection of [**MapRouteLeg**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636955) objects.

trans-unit.source: Access this collection through the [**Legs**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636973) property of the **MapRoute**.
trans-unit.target: Access this collection through the [**Legs**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636973) property of the **MapRoute**.

trans-unit.source: Each [**MapRouteLeg**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636955) contains a collection of [**MapRouteManeuver**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636961) objects.
trans-unit.target: Each [**MapRouteLeg**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636955) contains a collection of [**MapRouteManeuver**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636961) objects.

trans-unit.source: Access this collection through the [**Maneuvers**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636959) property of the **MapRouteLeg**.
trans-unit.target: Access this collection through the [**Maneuvers**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636959) property of the **MapRouteLeg**.

trans-unit.source: Display directions
trans-unit.target: Display directions

trans-unit.source: Get a driving or walking route and directions by calling the methods of the [**MapRouteFinder**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636938) class—for example, [**GetDrivingRouteAsync**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636943) or [**GetWalkingRouteAsync**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636953).
trans-unit.target: Get a driving or walking route and directions by calling the methods of the [**MapRouteFinder**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636938) class—for example, [**GetDrivingRouteAsync**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636943) or [**GetWalkingRouteAsync**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636953).

trans-unit.source: The [**MapRouteFinderResult**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636939) object contains a [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) object that you can access through its [**Route**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636940) property.
trans-unit.target: The [**MapRouteFinderResult**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636939) object contains a [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) object that you can access through its [**Route**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636940) property.

trans-unit.source: When you request a route, you can specify the following things:
trans-unit.target: When you request a route, you can specify the following things:

trans-unit.source: You can provide a start point and end point only, or you can provide a series of waypoints to compute the route.
trans-unit.target: You can provide a start point and end point only, or you can provide a series of waypoints to compute the route.

trans-unit.source: You can specify optimizations - for example, minimize the distance.
trans-unit.target: You can specify optimizations - for example, minimize the distance.

trans-unit.source: You can specify restrictions - for example, avoid highways.
trans-unit.target: You can specify restrictions - for example, avoid highways.

trans-unit.source: The computed [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) has properties that provide the time to traverse the route, the length of the route, and the collection of [**MapRouteLeg**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636955) objects that contain the legs of the route.
trans-unit.target: The computed [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) has properties that provide the time to traverse the route, the length of the route, and the collection of [**MapRouteLeg**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636955) objects that contain the legs of the route.

trans-unit.source: Each **MapRouteLeg** object contains a collection of [**MapRouteManeuver**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636961) objects.
trans-unit.target: Each **MapRouteLeg** object contains a collection of [**MapRouteManeuver**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636961) objects.

trans-unit.source: The **MapRouteManeuver** object contains directions that you can access through its [**InstructionText**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636964) property.
trans-unit.target: The **MapRouteManeuver** object contains directions that you can access through its [**InstructionText**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636964) property.

trans-unit.source: To display a [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) on a [**MapControl**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn637004), construct a [**MapRouteView**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn637122) with the **MapRoute**.
trans-unit.target: To display a [**MapRoute**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn636937) on a [**MapControl**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn637004), construct a [**MapRouteView**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn637122) with the **MapRoute**.

trans-unit.source: Then, add the **MapRouteView** to the [**Routes**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn637047) collection of the **MapControl**.
trans-unit.target: Then, add the **MapRouteView** to the [**Routes**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/dn637047) collection of the **MapControl**.
